K tool, version 3.0

Note: This file contains information regarding the stable release of the
K tool indicated above, regardless of whether it came with the release itself
or with subsequent nightly/latest builts.

What is new (from v2.7)
-----------------------

* The front-end is now implemented completely in Java (previously it was
implemented in a combination of Perl and Maude), making use of SDF (as
distributed with the Spoofax system).
